The lumberjack boots are a part of the Lumberjack clothing set dropped by Undead Lumberjacks in the Temple Trekking minigame. They increase experience by 0.2% when Woodcutting. This is increased to +2.5% when wearing the whole set.

Changes[edit | edit source]

Date Changes
14 March 2007
 Hotfix

The item was made obtainable as lumberjacks now drop the boots.

13 March 2007
(update)

The item was added to the game cache, but was unobtainable as Undead lumberjacks did not drop them due to a bug.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • The examine text is a reference to The Lumberjack Song by British comedy troupe Monty Python.
